{"tid":2331861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕不快樂","createTime":"2020-12-19T06:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T07:18:53.000Z","uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6246ba1878c6c9acfe0b05ab8893f401b40324","tid":2331861,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"仲有幾日就聖誕，唔知大家有咩節目呢<br />\n<br />\n係諗緊去邊到玩 食咩聖誕大餐既時候 <br />\n可唔可以諗埋佢地<span class=\"x-large\">12位手足</span><br />\n佢地到而家都仲係鹽田到<br />\n我地用少少時間 寫張聖誕咭比佢地好無<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCCCfaK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCCCfaK.png&h=d4082721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算班公安無真係交比佢地，我地都相信，<strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">12 位手足</span></span></strong> 會感受到我地無忘記過佢地 我地一直都有關注佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人會等佢地平安返黎"},{"pid":"a978679d9394164bfa0f13fce229f06def424d37","tid":2331861,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67bec64b3c8338f0ff67b15437aae3d507df8009","tid":2331861,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}